Package org.dudss.nodeshot.buildings

Game buildings.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Alertable
    A basic interface for a AbstractBuilding that can be alerted by a Package.
    Connectable
    A interface that identifies an AbstractBuilding that has a single Node that can be connected to the conveyor system.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractBuilding
    The basic skeletal representation of a building.
    AbstractGenerator
    Generator that spawns creeper
    AbstractIOPort
    An Input/Output building that consists of two tiles and can interact with an AbstractStorage and its storage.
    AbstractIOStorage
    An extended version of an AbstractStorage that can hold items in 2 separate item pools.
    AbstractMine
    Building that generates items at a rate.
    AbstractStorage
    Building that can accept and hold items in a single shared storage pool.
    AlertableBuilding
    Skeletal construction of a building that can be alerted by I/O Nodes.
